data.Description: I've lived in NYC for 10 years, and worked as a stand up comedian and a photographer. This year, I started doing walking tours in the city to combine my "crowd work" skills :D and photography into one business :) I enjoy making new friends, and connecting with people. Doing stand-up comedy for 10 years taught me how to break the ice in 2 seconds, so even if you get a little discomfort from a big camera lens, but still want great photos, I AM YOUR GAL. Together we'll have a stress free photoshoot, as we learn the history of the most beautiful neighborhoods in NYC. <3
